snippet.title: Dev Diary: What is Once Human
snippet.description: Once Human is a new weird sandbox survival game that gives players the freedom to explore and experience the world of Nalcott in whichever way they like. This video shows some game concepts about Once Human. If you're interested, you can find more info about this game on our official Twitter at https://twitter.com/OnceHuman_ or join our Discord server at https://discord.gg/oncehuman.
